00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,240
Hyah!

122
00:07:18,380 --> 00:07:23,959
(Nanzhao Border)

123
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:25,079
We can't put all our hopes

124
00:07:25,120 --> 00:07:26,680
