131
00:07:37,759 --> 00:07:39,360
and wipe out the Nanzhao delegation.

132
00:07:39,560 --> 00:07:40,199
Good.

133
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,160
You Chen'an is cunning,

134
00:07:42,399 --> 00:07:43,759
