135
00:07:45,279 --> 00:07:46,680
I have a plan

136
00:07:46,879 --> 00:07:47,680
to save Jing Yi,

137
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:50,240
but he'll have to suffer a bit.

138
00:07:57,519 --> 00:07:58,439
Are you saying

139
00:07:59,040 --> 00:08:00,920
the Great Tang will soon find out

140
00:08:01,480 --> 00:08:02,720
that you faked your death?

141
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:03,920
Yes.

142
00:08:04,720 --> 00:08:06,040
I feared the campaign would be delayed,

143
00:08:06,399 --> 00:08:07,639
