to enter the city.

155
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:35,200
Father,

156
00:08:36,960 --> 00:08:38,440
I'll lead a small unit

157
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,039
across the Jiaozhou border

158
00:08:40,559 --> 00:08:41,399
and the choke point.

159
00:08:45,679 --> 00:08:46,559
