161
00:08:59,879 --> 00:09:00,200
Come.

162
00:09:00,639 --> 00:09:01,399
Your Highness, please.

163
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:07,039
You're most thoughtful, Lord Li.

164
00:09:09,159 --> 00:09:10,440
I know you were coming,

165
00:09:10,759 --> 00:09:11,720
