173
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,879
Rather than liking it,

174
00:09:35,120 --> 00:09:36,399
it's more about remembrance.

175
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:41,679
I'm not capable enough

176
00:09:41,879 --> 00:09:42,799
