00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:47,799
Senior Jing,

281
00:14:48,399 --> 00:14:50,200
this is clearly slander!

282
00:14:50,279 --> 00:14:50,720
Enough.

283
00:14:51,639 --> 00:14:53,600
The truth will soon be clear.

284
00:14:53,879 --> 00:14:54,440
Jinbao.

285
00:14:54,450 --> 00:14:55,000
Yes, Your Majesty.

286
00:14:55,120 --> 00:14:56,440
Summon Jing Yi to the palace.

287
00:14:56,559 --> 00:14:57,000
Yes.

288
00:15:03,240 --> 00:15:03,799
He.

289
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:08,879
He.

290
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:11,679
He.

291
00:15:21,919 --> 00:15:23,559
(I may not return this time.)

292
00:15:24,399 --> 00:15:25,399
(Take care, all of you.)

293
00:15:26,279 --> 00:15:27,559
(I humbly ask Commandery Prince An)

294
00:15:28,279 --> 00:15:30,159
(to take care of Chu Chu
for the rest of her life.)

295
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:13,960
Yi!

296
00:16:14,240 --> 00:16:14,960
Yi!

297
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:15,799
Yi,

298
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:17,639
how did you end up hurt like this?

299
00:16:17,799 --> 00:16:18,519
Gao Luoqian,

300
00:16:19,519 --> 00:16:21,120
you dared to use torture!

301
00:16:21,600 --> 00:16:22,600
Have you forgotten

302
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,000
that you're still

303
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,679
in the Great Tang?

304
00:16:25,879 --> 00:16:27,240
I didn't do this, Your Majesty.

305
00:16:27,519 --> 00:16:29,240
I have no idea what happened.

306
00:16:29,960 --> 00:16:31,120
Wait, Vice Envoy Gao.

307
00:16:32,279 --> 00:16:33,000
What,

308
00:16:33,559 --> 00:16:36,080
did I beat myself like this?

309
00:16:37,840 --> 00:16:39,080
It was your wife.

310
00:16:39,159 --> 00:16:39,639
Come on.

311
00:16:39,799 --> 00:16:41,279
I was furious yesterday, yes.

312
00:16:41,559 --> 00:16:42,600
- But I only meant to scare you.
- Yes.

313
00:16:42,639 --> 00:16:43,440
Gao Luoqian,

314
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,000
how dare you!

315
00:16:49,840 --> 00:16:51,240
His Majesty ordered you
to keep watch,

316
00:16:51,919 --> 00:16:53,440
yet you hurt him without permission.

317
00:16:53,759 --> 00:16:55,000
I see.

318
00:16:55,759 --> 00:16:58,240
You and your wife staged a whole act,

319
00:16:58,279 --> 00:16:59,759
treating me like a fool?

320
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:03,039
Let me remind you,

321
00:17:04,279 --> 00:17:05,279
Senior Jing

322
00:17:05,359 --> 00:17:06,480
only has this one son.

323
00:17:07,279 --> 00:17:09,079
If he finds out that his only son

324
00:17:09,319 --> 00:17:10,960
was beaten by you,

325
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:13,920
I believe he'll stop at nothing
to settle accounts with you.

326
00:17:18,079 --> 00:17:20,519
Lady Jing, you're protective
of your husband.

327
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:23,000
How could I deny you that?

328
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:25,200
Since you're here,

329
00:17:26,200 --> 00:17:27,720
none of  you should leave.

330
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:31,240
I'll be sure to provide you both
with food and drink.

331
00:17:31,559 --> 00:17:32,680
What right do you have to detain me?

332
00:17:32,690 --> 00:17:34,290
I'm to keep Vice Minister Jing
under strict guard

333
00:17:34,319 --> 00:17:36,279
by imperial order.

334
00:17:36,599 --> 00:17:38,319
Lady Jing, you barge in so abruptly.

335
00:17:38,440 --> 00:17:41,079
You probably have coordinated
with Vice Minister Jing

336
00:17:41,240 --> 00:17:42,759
to pass messages out.

337
00:17:43,119 --> 00:17:44,079
Naturally,

338
00:17:45,039 --> 00:17:47,119
I can't let you go.

339
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:49,000
Watch them closely.

340
00:17:50,079 --> 00:17:50,799
Gao Luoqian!

341
00:17:51,039 --> 00:17:51,839
Gao Luoqian!

342
00:17:52,279 --> 00:17:53,000
Gao Luoqian!

343
00:17:53,599 --> 00:17:53,880
You!

344
00:17:53,920 --> 00:17:55,079
Looking back now,

345
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:58,000
Lady Jing showed up there on purpose.

346
00:17:58,400 --> 00:17:59,440
After I left,

347
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:01,319
it must've been Lady Jing

348
00:18:01,559 --> 00:18:02,759
who beat you into this state.

349
00:18:09,533 --> 00:18:10,599
Vice Envoy Gao,

350
00:18:11,160 --> 00:18:13,799
what's wrong with you?

351
00:18:14,559 --> 00:18:15,440
Your Majesty,

352
00:18:16,759 --> 00:18:18,079
Vice Envoy Gao insists

353
00:18:18,359 --> 00:18:21,319
that I conspired with Commandery Prince An
to kill Second Prince.

354
00:18:21,440 --> 00:18:22,079
So he attempted

355
00:18:22,440 --> 00:18:23,240
to force a confession.

356
00:18:23,279 --> 00:18:24,319
That is sheer fabrication!

357
00:18:24,480 --> 00:18:26,440
I trust the laws of the Great Tang.

358
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:27,319
How could I

359
00:18:27,599 --> 00:18:28,839
abuse my power for personal revenge?

360
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:30,599
On top of that,

361
00:18:31,400 --> 00:18:32,039
even if

362
00:18:32,160 --> 00:18:34,039
I torture you into confessing,

363
00:18:34,279 --> 00:18:35,400
once we stood before His Majesty,

364
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:36,880
the truth would still come out.

365
00:18:37,799 --> 00:18:39,160
Just like how you're slandering me

366
00:18:39,200 --> 00:18:40,799
right now.

367
00:18:40,839 --> 00:18:42,440
I have no reason to do such a thing.

368
00:18:44,599 --> 00:18:46,640
If it were only for Second Prince,

369
00:18:46,799 --> 00:18:48,599
you wouldn't have the reason.

370
00:18:49,359 --> 00:18:51,119
But I happened to hear

371
00:18:52,240 --> 00:18:53,279
that Vice Envoy Gao

372
00:18:53,720 --> 00:18:56,960
was connected to the poisonings
of Great Tang officials.

373
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:59,039
So you sought to

374
00:18:59,480 --> 00:19:01,200
silence witnesses.

375
00:19:01,839 --> 00:19:02,720
Is this true?

376
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:03,640
Slander!

377
00:19:04,559 --> 00:19:05,480
This is slander!

378
00:19:05,960 --> 00:19:06,720
Slander?

379
00:19:08,599 --> 00:19:10,599
Vice Envoy Gao, have you forgotten

380
00:19:11,559 --> 00:19:13,240
that you sold an apothecary
half a year ago?

381
00:19:17,920 --> 00:19:18,400
Your Majesty.

382
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:26,200
Half a year ago,

383
00:19:26,960 --> 00:19:28,599
Vice Envoy Gao sold an apothecary,

384
00:19:29,119 --> 00:19:30,839
and the clerk was left behind,
Chang Shou.

385
00:19:31,039 --> 00:19:32,759
He was one of the Nanzhao spies

386
00:19:33,000 --> 00:19:35,240
who sold poison in the poisoning cases.

387
00:19:38,720 --> 00:19:39,839
According to him,

388
00:19:40,759 --> 00:19:43,279
he acted under Vice Envoy Gao's orders.

389
00:19:43,559 --> 00:19:45,240
He disguised himself
and lay low in Chang'an,

390
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:46,960
waiting for chances to cause trouble.

391
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:49,599
Vice Envoy Gao,

392
00:19:50,960 --> 00:19:52,559
how do you explain this?

393
00:19:53,039 --> 00:19:54,039
Your Majesty,

394
00:19:55,039 --> 00:19:55,920
I

395
00:19:56,119 --> 00:19:57,839
sold an apothecary

396
00:19:57,920 --> 00:19:59,440
due to poor management.

397
00:19:59,839 --> 00:20:01,400
But as for Chang Shou,

398
00:20:01,599 --> 00:20:02,559
I knew nothing of him.

399
00:20:04,150 --> 00:20:05,880
No one would investigate
every clerk's background

400
00:20:06,359 --> 00:20:10,400
when running a business.

401
00:20:11,240 --> 00:20:11,880
Moreover,

402
00:20:12,359 --> 00:20:14,240
when the poisonings occurred,

403
00:20:14,519 --> 00:20:16,599
the apothecary had already been sold.

404
00:20:16,960 --> 00:20:18,880
If I remember correctly,

405
00:20:19,119 --> 00:20:20,680
the buyer who took it over

406
00:20:20,839 --> 00:20:23,559
was the elder brother
of Commandery Princess Consort An.

407
00:20:25,160 --> 00:20:26,279
If we speak of suspicion,

408
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:28,359
his is greater than mine.

409
00:20:28,720 --> 00:20:29,319
Must I confess

410
00:20:29,559 --> 00:20:31,240
to a fabricated crime

411
00:20:31,400 --> 00:20:33,279
based solely on a statement

412
00:20:33,799 --> 00:20:36,400
pieced together by Commandery Prince An?

413
00:20:38,920 --> 00:20:40,680
Right now, I indeed have no proof

414
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:43,039
to verify Chang Shou's words.

415
00:20:43,400 --> 00:20:44,359
Exactly.

416
00:20:44,559 --> 00:20:46,079
But as you said yourself,

417
00:20:46,599 --> 00:20:48,079
this concerns two states.

418
00:20:48,240 --> 00:20:49,480
Anyone with suspicion

419
00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:51,799
should first be detained.

420
00:20:52,759 --> 00:20:55,359
The Great Tang's laws
apply equally to all.

421
00:20:55,400 --> 00:20:57,160
Vice Minister Jing could comply,

422
00:20:57,359 --> 00:21:00,000
so should you.

423
00:21:02,799 --> 00:21:04,720
You killed Second Prince of Nanzhao,

424
00:21:04,839 --> 00:21:06,279
then you intend to
detain the vice envoy.

425
00:21:06,599 --> 00:21:07,319
Commandery Prince An.

426
00:21:08,079 --> 00:21:09,079
Vice Minister Jing.

427
00:21:09,440 --> 00:21:10,480
Aren't you afraid

428
00:21:10,759 --> 00:21:12,200
that your personal motives

429
00:21:12,759 --> 00:21:14,400
will escalate tensions

430
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:16,160
and make you sinners?

431
00:21:17,519 --> 00:21:19,599
I hadn't informed you

432
00:21:20,720 --> 00:21:22,720
that we've already obtained proof

433
00:21:23,440 --> 00:21:24,799
that Second Prince is still alive.

434
00:21:25,240 --> 00:21:26,119
What did you say?

435
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:28,000
Your Majesty,

436
00:21:28,920 --> 00:21:31,039
I request that the coroner
Chu Chu be summoned.

437
00:21:31,640 --> 00:21:32,200
Granted.

438
00:21:46,200 --> 00:21:46,720
Your Majesty,

439
00:21:47,279 --> 00:21:48,680
You Chen'an faked his death and escaped.

440
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:50,160
Not long ago, he returned to Nanzhao.

441
00:21:50,680 --> 00:21:52,000
The blood print here

442
00:21:52,519 --> 00:21:53,799
was left by his finger.

443
00:22:04,640 --> 00:22:06,119
What does

444
00:22:06,559 --> 00:22:07,519
a single fingerprint prove?

445
00:22:08,400 --> 00:22:09,279
This fingerprint

446
00:22:09,720 --> 00:22:11,079
perfectly matches the prints

447
00:22:11,119 --> 00:22:13,240
collected by the Three Judicial Offices.

448
00:22:13,599 --> 00:22:14,759
Who knows

449
00:22:14,839 --> 00:22:16,240
when this print appeared?

450
00:22:16,839 --> 00:22:19,279
Perhaps you obtained it
before killing him.

451
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:21,480
The bloodstains on the cloth
can be examined.

452
00:22:22,160 --> 00:22:23,039
This fingerprint

453
00:22:23,519 --> 00:22:25,160
is no more than three days old.

454
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:29,640
This is irrefutable evidence

455
00:22:30,559 --> 00:22:31,680
sent back by my brother, Chu He,

456
00:22:32,279 --> 00:22:33,359
from You Chen'an's side.

457
00:22:47,839 --> 00:22:49,440
Knowing the danger of this mission,

458
00:22:50,039 --> 00:22:52,039
my brother was prepared
to perish with the enemy.

459
00:22:52,650 --> 00:22:54,319
The carrier pigeon
that returned with his letter

460
00:22:54,400 --> 00:22:55,799
was stained in chaotic blood.

461
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:58,039
There must've been a fierce struggle

462
00:22:58,040 --> 00:22:59,520
when he took the fingerprint
from You Chen'an.

463
00:22:59,799 --> 00:23:00,880
In haste, he could only

464
00:23:00,920 --> 00:23:02,640
send back the fingerprint
and his final letter.

465
00:23:03,319 --> 00:23:05,000
My brother paid with his life

466
00:23:05,480 --> 00:23:06,880
for this proof.

467
00:23:17,119 --> 00:23:18,839
With witness and evidence both present,

468
00:23:19,480 --> 00:23:21,480
do you have anything else to say,
Vice Envoy Gao?

469
00:23:22,599 --> 00:23:23,839
This is all one-sided testimony.

470
00:23:24,759 --> 00:23:26,319
I will report this to my king.

471
00:23:26,720 --> 00:23:27,599
No need.

472
00:23:28,319 --> 00:23:30,000
Once your name is cleared

473
00:23:30,440 --> 00:23:31,759
and returns to Nanzhao,

474
00:23:31,799 --> 00:23:32,720
you may see for yourself

475
00:23:33,000 --> 00:23:34,720
whether You Chen'an is dead or alive.

476
00:23:35,200 --> 00:23:36,359
Vice Minister Jing is innocent.

477
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:37,440
Release him at once

478
00:23:37,480 --> 00:23:38,599
and restore him to office.

479
00:23:39,080 --> 00:23:40,000
The Three Judicial Offices

480
00:23:40,119 --> 00:23:42,599
uncovered the faked death
of Second Prince of Nanzhao.

481
00:23:42,600 --> 00:23:43,410
They should be rewarded.

482
00:23:43,880 --> 00:23:44,559
Gao Luoqian

483
00:23:45,599 --> 00:23:47,160
is suspected of planting spies

484
00:23:47,319 --> 00:23:49,000
and poisoning Great Tang officials.

485
00:23:49,359 --> 00:23:51,440
Order the Capital Prefecture,
from today onward,

486
00:23:51,680 --> 00:23:53,400
to seal the Nanzhao post station.

487
00:23:53,759 --> 00:23:55,200
Until the truth is found,

488
00:23:55,559 --> 00:23:57,599
no one is permitted to enter or leave.

489
00:24:16,420 --> 00:24:21,260
(Stele of Chu He of Great Tang)

490
00:24:21,260 --> 00:24:24,580
♪Time drips away
like fading crimson scent♪

491
00:24:24,580 --> 00:24:27,780
♪The hardships of arrival
pass in a fleeting blink♪

492
00:24:28,420 --> 00:24:31,020
♪Palm lines carry
the footprints of memory♪

493
00:24:32,160 --> 00:24:33,640
I'll risk my life

494
00:24:33,720 --> 00:24:35,160
just to teach him a lesson for you.

495
00:24:35,660 --> 00:24:39,300
♪If two hearts can fly as one
then storms are part of the way♪

496
00:24:39,300 --> 00:24:42,660
♪Looking back the sky
has already cleared♪

497
00:24:43,200 --> 00:24:44,000
Why talk about later?

498
00:24:44,200 --> 00:24:45,279
Go back and rest now.

499
00:24:50,359 --> 00:24:51,720
After leaving West Market, head east.

500
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:52,680
There's a pond there.

501
00:24:53,359 --> 00:24:54,359
I picked these fresh for you.

502
00:24:54,559 --> 00:24:56,480
I don't know
whether the lotus seeds in Chang'an

503
00:24:56,500 --> 00:24:57,839
taste better than those from Qianzhou.

504
00:25:00,880 --> 00:25:02,400
Gently does it.

505
00:25:03,279 --> 00:25:03,920
I brought all these

506
00:25:04,359 --> 00:25:05,599
all the way from Qianzhou,

507
00:25:05,920 --> 00:25:07,119
especially for my sister.

508
00:25:09,020 --> 00:25:12,060
♪Quietly waiting for rumors to fade♪

509
00:25:13,759 --> 00:25:15,000
(The journey was perilous.)

510
00:25:15,480 --> 00:25:16,480
(By the time you read this,)

511
00:25:17,119 --> 00:25:18,279
(I'm already gone.)

512
00:25:22,079 --> 00:25:23,319
(For my past mistakes,)

513
00:25:23,720 --> 00:25:24,799
(I'm filled with regret.)

514
00:25:25,680 --> 00:25:26,799
(Don't grieve for me.)

515
00:25:28,119 --> 00:25:29,279
(Live well.)

516
00:25:29,540 --> 00:25:34,140
♪The first breath upon awakening♪

517
00:25:34,500 --> 00:25:41,020
♪This bond will never waver, so we
stay together till our hair turns white♪

518
00:25:41,820 --> 00:25:49,380
♪I ask time itself to hold the pen,
and write the ending of eternity♪

519
00:26:04,300 --> 00:26:08,060
♪Rugged roads become the paths
of sun and moon♪

520
00:26:08,060 --> 00:26:11,100
♪Fireflies like stars
circle through the seasons♪

521
00:26:11,559 --> 00:26:12,839
I found this amulet

522
00:26:13,480 --> 00:26:14,839
under his pillow.

523
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:17,359
He wrapped it in a handkerchief.

524
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:19,240
He must've treasured it dearly

525
00:26:20,680 --> 00:26:22,160
and didn't take it with him to Nanzhao.

526
00:26:22,900 --> 00:26:25,900
♪Quietly waiting for rumors to fade♪

527
00:26:26,260 --> 00:26:33,140
♪Together we face the tides of fate,
turning the course of heaven and earth♪

528
00:26:35,319 --> 00:26:36,400
Do you know?

529
00:26:38,359 --> 00:26:40,920
I prayed for this
with my first month's pay,

530
00:26:44,680 --> 00:26:46,680
yet it couldn't keep him safe.

531
00:26:50,400 --> 00:26:51,480
What mattered most to him

532
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:55,160
was your sincerity.

533
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:57,160
These past few days,

534
00:27:00,880 --> 00:27:02,920
I've kept dreaming of
when we were still in Qianzhou.

535
00:27:04,400 --> 00:27:06,599
If he hadn't been worried about me,

536
00:27:07,799 --> 00:27:09,119
he wouldn't have come to Chang'an.

537
00:27:09,450 --> 00:27:10,279
And none of this would've...

538
00:27:16,039 --> 00:27:17,079
He gave his life

539
00:27:18,279 --> 00:27:19,240
not only for you,

540
00:27:20,079 --> 00:27:21,240
but also for the greater cause.

541
00:27:22,279 --> 00:27:23,599
So take good care of yourself.

542
00:27:24,279 --> 00:27:25,599
Only then can he rest in peace.

543
00:27:27,960 --> 00:27:29,920
The chance he brought with his life

544
00:27:31,519 --> 00:27:32,559
will never be wasted.

545
00:27:39,640 --> 00:27:41,000
I'll let this amulet

546
00:27:41,759 --> 00:27:43,720
stay with him.

547
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:45,480
May he find joy and peace

548
00:27:46,240 --> 00:27:47,440
in his next life.

549
00:27:54,200 --> 00:27:55,079
Throw it back to him.

550
00:27:55,599 --> 00:27:57,039
Don't bring every trivial thing to me.

551
00:28:00,960 --> 00:28:01,359
Madam.

552
00:28:04,839 --> 00:28:06,279
What's so serious

553
00:28:06,440 --> 00:28:08,079
that you're sighing?

554
00:28:09,200 --> 00:28:10,319
You're here.

555
00:28:11,519 --> 00:28:13,599
How can I not sigh?

556
00:28:14,759 --> 00:28:16,119
You don't know.

557
00:28:16,240 --> 00:28:18,359
The Capital Prefecture

558
00:28:19,160 --> 00:28:21,839
is cleaning up all the mess
for the Three Judicial Offices.

559
00:28:22,240 --> 00:28:24,480
They give me endless trouble every day.

