561
00:28:27,400 --> 00:28:28,680
Just keep your distance.

562
00:28:28,960 --> 00:28:29,440
Distance?

563
00:28:29,759 --> 00:28:30,599
How?

564
00:28:31,680 --> 00:28:33,200
I can't.

