00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:53,119
I...

574
00:28:56,279 --> 00:28:57,599
Enough.

575
00:28:59,640 --> 00:29:01,880
You just deal with it for now.

576
00:29:02,079 --> 00:29:04,240
Get through this safely
and step down in peace.

577
00:29:04,680 --> 00:29:06,599
Don't end up being sent away
from the capital.

578
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:12,240
Do you hear me?

579
00:29:12,839 --> 00:29:14,680
I do.

580
00:29:15,039 --> 00:29:16,599
I'll listen to everything you say.

581
00:29:16,920 --> 00:29:17,920
Just one word.

582
00:29:19,359 --> 00:29:20,680
Endure.

583
00:29:30,200 --> 00:29:32,160
Although Gao Luoqian
is now under our control,

584
00:29:33,240 --> 00:29:34,640
for him to pull off so many misdeeds

585
00:29:34,720 --> 00:29:36,200
in the capital,

586
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:39,400
he must've had help
from local officials.

587
00:29:39,960 --> 00:29:41,400
These people

588
00:29:41,759 --> 00:29:43,200
are a hidden danger in the Great Tang.

589
00:29:43,599 --> 00:29:45,000
The more you think about it,

590
00:29:45,559 --> 00:29:46,880
the more chilling it feels.

591
00:29:47,680 --> 00:29:49,680
We thought everything
was calm and smooth,

592
00:29:50,000 --> 00:29:50,839
but the enemy's claws

593
00:29:51,559 --> 00:29:52,519
have long been driven

594
00:29:53,279 --> 00:29:55,440
deep into the Great Tang.

595
00:29:55,880 --> 00:29:56,480
I remember

596
00:29:56,559 --> 00:29:58,240
when you were tracking down You Chen'an,

597
00:29:58,480 --> 00:30:01,200
you once ran into officials from
the Capital Prefecture searching as well.

