00:30:01,519 --> 00:30:02,319
But they

599
00:30:02,400 --> 00:30:04,480
never reported their findings
to the Three Judicial Offices.

600
00:30:05,799 --> 00:30:06,200
Exactly.

601
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:09,480
I ran into him at a post station
outside the capital.

602
00:30:10,920 --> 00:30:12,640
He was chatting happily
with Gao Luoqian.

603
00:30:14,559 --> 00:30:15,720
What were they doing there?

604
00:30:16,079 --> 00:30:18,839
They were looking nearby for suspects.

605
00:30:19,799 --> 00:30:21,240
Do you know what they talked about?

606
00:30:23,319 --> 00:30:26,039
My memory isn't good.

607
00:30:35,480 --> 00:30:37,160
Ah, I remember now.

608
00:30:37,599 --> 00:30:38,759
That foreigner

609
00:30:38,839 --> 00:30:40,240
told the officer

610
00:30:40,279 --> 00:30:44,079
to expand the search area
and report back to him promptly.

611
00:30:44,480 --> 00:30:47,200
A few officials traveling through
were lodged at the post station.

612
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:48,559
They heard them.

613
00:30:49,200 --> 00:30:50,039
I asked them all.

614
00:30:50,040 --> 00:30:51,990
Their accounts matched
what the post station officer said.

615
00:30:52,839 --> 00:30:54,000
Then there's only one possibility.

616
00:30:55,559 --> 00:30:56,519
You mean...

617
00:30:56,960 --> 00:30:58,920
The Capital Prefecture
is colluding with them.

618
00:30:59,100 --> 00:31:01,660
(Capital Prefecture)

619
00:31:14,780 --> 00:31:17,620
(Capital Prefecture Seal)

620
00:31:18,079 --> 00:31:20,079
The Capital Prefecture
is colluding with Nanzhao?

621
00:31:20,359 --> 00:31:22,000
Do you realize what you're saying?

622
00:31:22,359 --> 00:31:24,000
I wish we were wrong.

623
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:26,119
Jiang Daohai has never
gotten along with me.

624
00:31:26,279 --> 00:31:28,599
Ever since I proposed sending censors

625
00:31:28,640 --> 00:31:29,680
to each province,

