00:31:32,839 --> 00:31:34,480
Jiang Daohai is close to them.

628
00:31:35,400 --> 00:31:37,880
After that, whether it was
the serial murders at the Music Office,

629
00:31:38,240 --> 00:31:39,640
the capital's security issues,

630
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:42,839
or spreading rumors

631
00:31:43,359 --> 00:31:44,559
about my illness,

632
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:47,319
he may well have been behind it.

