Jiaozhou is sending troops.

636
00:31:54,400 --> 00:31:55,960
Nanzhao will surely try every way

637
00:31:56,279 --> 00:31:58,200
to drag the Great Tang
into a worse position.

638
00:31:58,759 --> 00:31:59,559
Next,

