no matter how much noise they make,

642
00:32:10,279 --> 00:32:12,000
it could merely be driven
by personal ambition.

643
00:32:12,680 --> 00:32:16,200
But if Nanzhao colludes
with Great Tang officials

644
00:32:16,559 --> 00:32:17,799
and sows discord in Chang'an,

645
00:32:18,920 --> 00:32:20,720
then they want only one thing.

646
00:32:22,000 --> 00:32:22,759
The nation.

647
00:32:39,200 --> 00:32:39,799
Your Majesty,

