717
00:35:43,480 --> 00:35:44,719
Rest assured.

718
00:35:44,880 --> 00:35:47,239
We only have one last favor to ask.

719
00:35:47,599 --> 00:35:48,840
Once it's done,

720
00:35:48,920 --> 00:35:50,440
everything ends.

721
00:35:51,280 --> 00:35:52,199
Speak.

722
00:35:55,719 --> 00:35:57,199
Please take the trouble

723
00:35:58,039 --> 00:35:59,480
