739
00:36:43,199 --> 00:36:45,039
There is a mole
in the Capital Prefecture?

740
00:36:46,239 --> 00:36:47,400
I'm not sure about the others,

741
00:36:47,599 --> 00:36:50,360
but Jiang Daohai would never dare
