cooperate with me.

745
00:37:02,119 --> 00:37:03,519
Prevention is better than a cure.

746
00:37:04,000 --> 00:37:05,119
If there is a hidden disease,

747
00:37:05,559 --> 00:37:08,599
you must root it out
before it grows into something grave.

748
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:09,760
Only then can there be peace.

749
00:37:10,559 --> 00:37:11,559
If you keep delaying,

750
00:37:11,719 --> 00:37:13,800
and the illness breaks out
for all to see,

751
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:16,079
then even an immortal couldn't save it.

752
00:37:17,440 --> 00:37:18,480
If Prefect Jiang

753
00:37:19,199 --> 00:37:20,360
is innocent,

754
00:37:21,039 --> 00:37:23,000
the Three Judicial Offices
would never allow anyone

755
00:37:23,039 --> 00:37:23,800
to wrong him.

756
00:37:34,760 --> 00:37:35,320
Well.

757
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:37,599
At this point,

758
00:37:38,440 --> 00:37:39,840
I don't wish to cover for him.

759
00:37:40,559 --> 00:37:41,719
I don't know about other matters,

760
00:37:42,199 --> 00:37:43,280
but there is one thing.

761
00:37:43,719 --> 00:37:45,480
If someone were to seize this weakness,

