815
00:39:45,880 --> 00:39:47,519
Conventional tactics won't work.

816
00:39:47,840 --> 00:39:48,480
But

817
00:39:48,679 --> 00:39:51,559
a swift action tactic
couldn't be more suitable now.

818
00:39:52,519 --> 00:39:53,519
Someone has proposed

819
00:39:53,880 --> 00:39:55,320
that you lead a small unit,

820
00:39:55,440 --> 00:39:58,480
strike the Tang border,
seize the gorge,

821
00:39:58,599 --> 00:39:59,360
and hold it.

